{"tid":769428,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKU Hall警世文] 請你諗清楚先好入","createTime":"2018-08-06T07:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T07:24:04.000Z","uid":136583,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f566522ae9d0fc5839f3d0f0947360bcfaf17bc","tid":769428,"uid":136583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"老實講 如果只係為咗有個床位瞓教，我會勸你唔入hall好過入。<br />\n<br />\n見過太多撻皮嘅人hea住join hall function，為求攞contribution分，freeride嗰啲真正有心搞hall嘅人，無建設不特止好多時仲搞破壞，辛苦自己時又辛苦埋其他人。<br />\n<br />\n好多人話大學係社會嘅縮影，我就話hall就係其中嘅濃縮版。你或者可以識到志同道合嘅朋友、遇到一生嘅摯愛，同時亦都可以碰上不少閪人，見盡人性醜惡。 Come on 大學生，呢個社會就係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住hall就係一個give and take嘅過程，雖然你嘅付出同回報未必成正比，但係唔付出就想有回報仲有無天理？<br />\n<br />\n最後戴返個靚頭盔，呢個post唔係導人入hall，大學除左hall life之外亦都好多選擇。不過如果你揀咗入hall/ 想入hall，勸你真係有心先好入。It's time to grow，請為自己嘅選擇負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 二村current<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468f036379abf7a3c2c84fd1f8e9d00d59390d5c","tid":769428,"uid":136583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:22:41.000Z","msg":"歡迎討論/ 提問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0313a7d86641fdd8cf12f91fbc4fa7135bf252c2","tid":769428,"uid":66324,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:23:57.000Z","msg":"點解住hall唔可以淨係想搵張牀訓? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd96be212f2c21b0ebd84a8171d5144f82b1063","tid":769428,"uid":153456,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:24:58.000Z","msg":"點解住hall一定要係有心有貢獻<br />\n住得遠先嚟住常專心讀個書又要畀人話頹摺毒"},{"pid":"e4615e77361c3b6dbae2e1e2cc593d06f8a655fa","tid":769428,"uid":153456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T07:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解住hall一定要係有心有貢獻<br />\n住得遠先嚟住想專心讀個書又要畀人話頹摺毒</blockquote>"},{"pid"